snippet: A former manager of the Tick Tock Diner in Clifton, New Jersey, pleaded guilty on Monday to hiring a hit man to murder his uncle, who co-owns the popular eatery, prosecutors said....

headline.print_headline: Manager of New Jersey Diner Pleads Guilty in Murder for Hire Plot
headline.main: Manager of New Jersey Diner Pleads Guilty in Murder for Hire Plot

lead_paragraph: A former manager of the Tick Tock Diner in Clifton, New Jersey, pleaded guilty on Monday to hiring a hit man to murder his uncle, who co-owns the popular eatery, prosecutors said.
